Achievements.Name: The Whole Shebang
Achievements.Description: Earn every achievement in NBA 2K12.

Achievements.Name: Dawn of an Era
Achievements.Description: Get drafted as a lottery pick in the NBA draft in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: Money Bags
Achievements.Description: Purchase 3,000 skill points in a single transaction in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: Check!
Achievements.Description: Complete all 3 in-game objectives in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: Come Fly with Me
Achievements.Description: Purchase Michael Jordan's dunk package (His Airness) in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: NBA Cares
Achievements.Description: Make a donation to the NBA Cares global community outreach initiative in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: My Player of the Game
Achievements.Description: Be named Player of the Game (in an NBA game) in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: My Every Day Player
Achievements.Description: Become a starter in the NBA in My Player Mode.

Achievements.Name: I'm Worth It
Achievements.Description: Land a contract that pays at least $10M per season in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: My Big Eight-O
Achievements.Description: Earn an 80 overall rating in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: My All-Star
Achievements.Description: Be named an NBA All-Star in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: Immortality
Achievements.Description: Make the Hall of Fame in My Player mode.

Achievements.Name: Buzzer Beater
Achievements.Description: Make a game winning shot with no time left on the clock, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Trip-Dub
Achievements.Description: Record a triple double with any player, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Dub-Dub
Achievements.Description: Record two double doubles with any teammates, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Five by Five
Achievements.Description: Record 5 or more in 5 different stats with any player in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: It's Raining
Achievements.Description: Make 15 or more 3-pointers with any team, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Block Party
Achievements.Description: Record 10 or more blocks with any team, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Men of Steal
Achievements.Description: Record 10 or more steals with any team, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Swat and Swipe
Achievements.Description: Record at least 5 blocks and 5 steals with any team, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Smothering
Achievements.Description: Hold the opposing team's FG% below 40% with any team, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Giveth and Taketh Away
Achievements.Description: Record 10 or more rebounds and assists with any player, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Hold the Fat Lady
Achievements.Description: Start the 4th period losing by 10 or more points and win with any team, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Wire to Wire
Achievements.Description: Do not allow your opponent to lead the game at any point with any team, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: 4-Point Line
Achievements.Description: Pull off a successful 4-point play with any player, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: G Prime
Achievements.Description: End the 1st period with a 15 point lead or greater on the Hall of Fame difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: The Closer
Achievements.Description: Hold the opposing team to 0 points in the final two minutes of regulation, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: G Performance
Achievements.Description: Score at least 48 points with Kevin Durant to set a new career high, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: A 2K to Call My Own
Achievements.Description: Create a My2K Account.

Achievements.Name: G Recovery
Achievements.Description: Play an entire game using manual substitutions, in a non-simulated game.

Achievements.Name: Not Your Father's Association
Achievements.Description: Join an Online Association.

Achievements.Name: Another Day, Another Win
Achievements.Description: Win 5 NBA Today matchups.

Achievements.Name: Don't Hate the Player
Achievements.Description: Win the championship in an Online Association.

Achievements.Name: Streaking
Achievements.Description: Win 5 games in a row in The Association mode (playing all 5 games).

Achievements.Name: Home Court
Achievements.Description: Earn the NBA's best record in The Association mode (at least 30 games played).

Achievements.Name: Ticker Tape
Achievements.Description: Win an NBA Championship in The Association mode (playing every playoff game).

Achievements.Name: Shooting Star
Achievements.Description: Win the MVP award in NBA: Creating a Legend mode.

Achievements.Name: Sprite Slam Cam
Achievements.Description: Get the Sprite Slam Cam replay after a dunk with LeBron James.

Achievements.Name: Birthday
Achievements.Description: Create-a-Player.

Achievements.Name: Hey Mr. DJ
Achievements.Description: Create a 2K Beats Playlist.

Achievements.Name: This One Counts
Achievements.Description: Win one online ranked match.

Achievements.Name: Back to Back to Back
Achievements.Description: Win 3 ranked matches in a row.

Achievements.Name: You're Officially Hot
Achievements.Description: Win 5 ranked matches in a row.

Achievements.Name: Lincoln
Achievements.Description: Win 5 ranked matches total.

Achievements.Name: Hamilton
Achievements.Description: Win 10 ranked matches total.

Achievements.Name: Made My Name
Achievements.Description: Complete 5 of the NBA's Greatest challenges.

Achievements.Name: Left My Mark
Achievements.Description: Complete 10 of the NBA's Greatest challenges.

Achievements.Name: Wrote My Legend
Achievements.Description: Complete all 15 of the NBA's Greatest challenges.

Achievements.Name: The Sum of Its Parts
Achievements.Description: Play a Team Up Game.

Achievements.Name: It's Better to Give
Achievements.Description: Share any file type through 2K Share.
